00:18:57.900 --> 00:18:59.816
ANDREW LO: The one where
the line is tangent--

00:18:59.816 --> 00:19:02.910
so you're talking about
right around here, right?

00:19:02.910 --> 00:19:04.380
Somewhere here.

00:19:04.380 --> 00:19:08.190
That's where the line is
just tangent to that curve.

00:19:08.190 --> 00:19:10.050
Now why is that?

00:19:10.050 --> 00:19:11.388
How'd you come up with that?

00:19:11.388 --> 00:19:12.131
Yeah?

00:19:12.131 --> 00:19:14.256
AUDIENCE: If you took
anything below that then it'd

00:19:14.256 --> 00:19:17.124
be, I would say,
