00:31:52.004 --> 00:31:52.980
and we get vice versa.

00:31:52.980 --> 00:31:57.082
Just that we mention
[INAUDIBLE] different countries,

00:31:57.082 --> 00:32:00.435
in different economic regions,
in different industry,

00:32:00.435 --> 00:32:01.740
and they should not be--

00:32:01.740 --> 00:32:03.990
ANDREW LO: Let's actually
spend a little bit more time

00:32:03.990 --> 00:32:05.020
thinking about this.

00:32:05.020 --> 00:32:07.770
I want you guys to tell
me right now, give me

00:32:07.770 --> 00:32:12.440
a stock that you would put
your money in right now, today.

00:32:12.440 --> 00:32:17.640
S&amp;P has gone down by 45% since
