00:33:41.090 --> 00:33:42.230
AUDIENCE: Wal-Mart.

00:33:42.230 --> 00:33:43.890
ANDREW LO: Wal-Mart?

00:33:43.890 --> 00:33:45.255
AUDIENCE: It's been going up.

00:33:45.255 --> 00:33:47.130
