of analysis.

00:39:37.444 --> 00:39:39.110
But I'm going to get
to that at the end.

00:39:39.110 --> 00:39:41.500
So if I don't, please
bring it up again.

00:39:41.500 --> 00:39:43.390
I want to make a
comment about that,

00:39:43.390 --> 00:39:46.630
and how you can take this
relatively simple static theory

00:39:46.630 --> 00:39:49.240
and make it dynamic
in an informal way

00:39:49.240 --> 00:39:51.790
even though the analytics
become very hard when

00:39:51.790 --> 00:39:54.640
you try to do it formally.

00:39:54.640 --> 00:39:58.840
So the key points of this
